Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.14,0:00:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.01,0:00:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小諒　把自己的行李拿開
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.65,0:00:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好～

